      "content": "i don't know, it just feels like a bribe or something. like, instead of dealing with my questions, they just gave me this shiny new title to keep me quiet and under their thumb. it's like they're trying to \"reward\" me into being a team player. you don't think it's more likely they're just trying to keep an eye on me now that i'm in a higher position?",
